                <text type="forecast">Partly cloudy. Slight chance of a shower. Winds west to northwesterly 15 to 25 km/h turning southwesterly 15 to 20 km/h in the afternoon. Overnight temperatures falling to around 12 with daytime temperatures reaching the low to mid 20s.</text>
